<Page title="Privacy Policy" description="Fudgeboop privacy policy covering data collection, cookies, affiliate links, and third-party services.">
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 17 March 2026</p>

  <p>
    Fudgeboop ("we", "us", "our") operates the website <a href="https://fudgeboop.com">fudgeboop.com</a>.
    This Privacy Policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your data.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

  <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
  <p>When you visit our site, our hosting provider may automatically collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>IP address (anonymised where possible)</li>
    <li>Browser type and version</li>
    <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
    <li>Referring URL</li>
    <li>Device type and operating system</li>
  </ul>
  <p>This data is used solely for site analytics and performance monitoring. We do not use this data to personally identify you.</p>

  <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
  <p>If you contact us via email, we collect the information you provide in your message (e.g. name, email address, message content). We use this only to respond to your enquiry.</p>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    Our site may use essential cookies required for the website to function. We do not use advertising cookies or tracking cookies for targeted advertising.
  </p>
  <p>Third-party services embedded on our site (such as Pinterest widgets) may set their own cookies. These are governed by the respective third party's cookie policy.</p>

  <h2>Affiliate Links &amp; Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>
    Our content contains affiliate links to products and services. When you click these links, you may be directed to third-party websites (such as Amazon, Backcountry, REI, and others) that have their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review their policies before making a purchase.
  </p>
  <p>We participate in the following affiliate programmes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — Amazon's affiliate programme. Amazon may collect data when you click through from our site. See <a href="https://www.amazon.com/gp/help/customer/display.html?nodeId=GX7NJQ4ZB8MHFRNJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Amazon's Privacy Notice</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>ShareASale / Awin</strong> — Affiliate networks connecting us to various retailers.</li>
    <li>Other affiliate programmes as disclosed on individual posts.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Pinterest</h2>
  <p>
    We use the Pinterest API to publish and manage content on Pinterest. Pinterest may collect data about interactions with our pins. See <a href="https://policy.pinterest.com/en/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Pinterest's Privacy Policy</a>.
  </p>
  <p>We have verified our domain with Pinterest for Rich Pins functionality. This does not grant Pinterest access to any additional user data from our website.</p>

  <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties except:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>When required by law or legal process</li>
    <li>To our hosting provider for site operation</li>
    <li>Through affiliate link clicks (as described above), where the receiving merchant handles the transaction</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Retention</h2>
  <p>Server logs are retained for a maximum of 90 days. Contact form messages are retained until your enquiry is resolved, then deleted within 30 days.</p>

  <h2>Your Rights</h2>
  <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
    <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
    <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
    <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <strong>privacy@fudgeboop.com</strong>.</p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>Our site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

  <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last updated" date.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>For privacy-related enquiries, email us at <strong>privacy@fudgeboop.com</strong>.</p>
</Page>
